    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm just wondering why certain groups think it should be taught in school at all. like, is there a reason why some people think this is something that *needs* to be part of the official curriculum rather than just something kids learn at home? it feels like a pretty big jump from regular school subjects.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
