    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. i guess my concern is that when schools push these specific viewpoints, it kind of undermines the parents' role in teaching these values. do you think it's fair for a school to decide what's \"essential\" information when it's something so personal and controversial that many families have very different moral views on it?",
